[[Afaylu:Apuleius2.png|thumb|right|afulay]]'''Afulay'''  (s [[Tutlayt Talatint|tlatint]] :''-{Lucius Apuleius}-'', s [[tafransist|tfṛansist]]: ''-{Apuleus}-'' ) iga amsunaw amaziɣ ilul ɣ tɣrmt n [[Madur]] ɣ [[Suq Ahras]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Dzayr]] ɣ usggas n 125.
Ismun kigan n wannarn n tussna zun d taflsaft, tastrunumit, asujji n tskla. ikka-tt-inn ar isawal s tutlayt [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tamaziɣt]] d [[Tutlayt Talatint|tlatint]]. Immut ɣ usggas n 170. Ittwassn ufulay s idlisn nns nna dar illa watig imqqurn ɣ umaḍal zun d: "asnus n wurɣ" d "midisinilma" d "astranumika".

== Idlisn nns ==

=== Asnus n wurɣ ===
Asnus n wurɣ (s tlatinit: Asinus aureus)، tga ungal akumidi yara-t ufulay، tga ungal amzwaru ɣ [[Amzruy|umzruy]] n [[Afgan|ufgan]]. Adlis n Asnus n wurɣ illa gis 11 n tnfust n ufgan iẓlin s umiyn .

